Package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.alloc.proxy

Class SpinWSHandler

java.lang.Object
org.springframework.web.socket.handler.AbstractWebSocketHandler
org.springframework.web.socket.handler.BinaryWebSocketHandler
uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.alloc.proxy.SpinWSHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
HandshakeInterceptor, WebSocketHandler
@Component
public class SpinWSHandler
extends BinaryWebSocketHandler
implements HandshakeInterceptor
Initial handler for web sockets. Maps a particular websocket to a proxy handler that processes messages received and sends messages the other way.
Author:
Donal Fellows
